    <content lang="en">
      <city>Bern</city>
      <title>Federal Council adopts amendment of ordinances on assessment of goods in tourist traffic</title>
      <lead>A revision of the Customs Ordinance and Agra-Introduction Ordinance will simplify the assessment of goods in tourist traffic and speed up the crossing of borders. The ordinance amendments approved by the Federal Council at its meeting today will enter into force on 1 July 2014.</lead>
      <text link="no">This whole press release is available as a document in pdf format.</text>
